Parameters:
c1 - The first column of input file.
c2 - The second column of input file.
c3 - The third column of input file.
c4 - The fourth column of input file.
c5 - The fifth column of input file.
sr - The sixth column of input file, i.e. the short read. If it contains characters that are neither A, C, G nor T, then an exception is thrown.
q - The seventh column of input file, i.e. the quality.
